==  关闭雅虎地球村 ==
[[雅虎地球村|地球村]]是一个十分受欢迎的[[网站托管服务|网站托管服务]]，成立于1994年。在当时，它曾名列最热门网站的前三位。<ref>{{cite web|title=archiveteam|url=http://archiveteam.org/index.php?title=Geocities|access-date=2015-09-29|archive-date=2011-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110701085803/http://archiveteam.org/index.php?title=Geocities|dead-url=no}}</ref>雅虎于1999年收购-{}-并将其命名为“雅虎地球村”。十年后即2009年，雅虎决定将其关闭<ref>{{cite web|title=GeoCities Closing|url=http://help.yahoo.com/l/us/yahoo/geocities/close/|access-date=2015-09-29|archive-date=2009-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091018205426/http://help.yahoo.com/l/us/yahoo/geocities/close/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，删除其中数以百万的页面<ref>{{cite news|title=GeoCities' time has expired, Yahoo closing the site today|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2009/10/geocities-closing.html|work=The Los Angeles Times|date=2009-10-26|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2012-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121221025310/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/technology/2009/10/geocities-closing.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2009年9月，即正式关闭的一个月前，雅虎收到了10477049个使用者的信函，对其关闭服务相当遗憾。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://siteanalytics.compete.com/geocities.com/ |title=Site Analytics |access-date=2015-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160124181838/https://siteanalytics.compete.com/geocities.com/ |archive-date=2016-01-24 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

== 2010年雅虎群组改版 ==
2010年雅虎宣布对旗下的群组功能进行改版，但这次改版受到了大多数用户的不满和指责。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://techcrunch.com/2010/09/11/yahoo-mimics-facebook-with-groups-update-users-retaliate/ |title=Yahoo! Groups remodel |access-date=2015-09-29 |archive-date=2020-11-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127212719/https://techcrunch.com/2010/09/11/yahoo-mimics-facebook-with-groups-update-users-retaliate/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>2010年9月29日，雅虎社区副总裁吉姆·斯托纳姆宣布，将会根据用户的反馈，撤回原有的改版方案。<ref>[http://www.ygroupsblog.com/blog/?p=958 Latest Update on Our Changes | Yahoo! Groups Blog] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ygroupsblog.com/blog/?p=958 |date=20131224103758 }}. Ygroupsblog.com (2010-09-29). Retrieved on 2013-06-16.</ref>

== 2013年Flickr新功能争议 ==
2013年5月20日，雅虎旗下的图像和视频存放网站Flickr推出了重新设计的布局和额外的功能，包括1TB免费存储容量、无缝相册、封面照片功能和新式Android应用程序等等。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://techcrunch.com/2013/05/20/flickr-gets-a-huge-revamp-with-hi-res-image-filled-ui-new-android-app-and-1tb-of-free-storage/|title=Flickr Gets A Huge Revamp With Hi-Res Image-Filled UI, New Android App, And 1TB Of Free Storage|date=2013-05-20|last=Crook|first=Jordan|work=[[TechCrunch|TechCrunch]]|accessdate=2013-05-21|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123195026/https://techcrunch.com/2013/05/20/flickr-gets-a-huge-revamp-with-hi-res-image-filled-ui-new-android-app-and-1tb-of-free-storage/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="CNET">{{cite web|url=http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57585276-93/yahoo-wants-to-make-flickr-awesome-again/|title=Yahoo Wants to Make Flickr 'Awesome Again'|first=Shara|last=Tibken|work=[[CNET|CNET]]|date=2013-05-20|accessdate=2013-05-21|archive-date=2013-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130816170007/http://news.cnet.com/8301-1023_3-57585276-93/yahoo-wants-to-make-flickr-awesome-again/|dead-url=no}}</ref>最新一次改版将分享功能放置在中心位置，并且去除了该服务顶部的雅虎工具条。图片之间不再有空隙，而是紧密连在一起，并且当把光标置于上面时会自动放大。新页面上的文字和按钮也大幅减少，只保留了一些浮动文本信息，并增加了评论内容。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://chinese.engadget.com/2013/05/22/flickr-update-hands-on/|language=zh-hant|title=Flickr 大改版動手玩與付費方案分析：笑吧你！免費使用者|publisher=engadget中文|date=2013-05-22|accessdate=2015-09-29|archive-date=2020-02-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200221020158/http://chinese.engadget.com/2013/05/22/flickr-update-hands-on/|dead-url=no}}</ref>雅虎称此次的改动是一次“巨变”。<ref>{{cite web|first=Gary|last=Marshall|url=http://www.techradar.com/news/world-of-tech/photography-video-capture/new-flickr-has-yahoo-lost-its-mind--1153038|title=New Flickr: Has Yahoo Lost Its Mind?|work=[[TechRadar|TechRadar]]|date=2013-05-21|accessdate=2013-05-21|archive-date=2019-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190522041030/https://www.techradar.com/news/world-of-tech/photography-video-capture/new-flickr-has-yahoo-lost-its-mind--1153038|dead-url=no}}</ref>然而许多网友批评此次改动，雅虎官方网站的帮助论坛在之后不久收到了数千条的负面评论。<ref>{{cite web |last=Shaw |first=Gillian |url=http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2013/05/21/busy-monday-for-yahoo-acquires-tumblr-announces-flickr-overhaul/ |title=Yahoo Acquires Tumblr, Announces Flickr Overhaul |work=[[Vancouver_Sun|Vancouver Sun]] |date=2013-05-17 |accessdate=2013-05-23 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303220457/http://blogs.vancouversun.com/2013/05/21/busy-monday-for-yahoo-acquires-tumblr-announces-flickr-overhaul/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

